#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:169
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are entering the territory of the Zoltans.These creatures are not famous"
" for the reputation of good Samaritans, distributing everything just like "
"that.But here you can always be sure of a fair court."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:170
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The Contributes guard their boundaries and miss you only if the ID "
"federation is available.Let's hope they are not so courteous with the "
"rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:171
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You arrived in the space of the Zoltans.As far as you heard, they expected "
"the upcoming war and prepared to hold their boundaries."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:172
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Here, on the territory of the Zoltans, you are far from the home space of "
"the federation, and it is unclear whether the authorities will be favorable "
"to you.However, you must move on."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:173
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You arrived in the Zoltans sector.These humanoids saturated with energy are "
"sometimes too fair, but do not even think that it will bypass you.Here you "
"have equal rights with other races, despite belonging to the Federation."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:174
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive in the Zoltans sector.You can be sure that you will find high "
"-tech weapons in their stores.Or maybe you will be destroyed by this weapon "
"..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:175
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"The inscription at the lighthouse at the entrance to the Zoltantsev sector "
"says: “Long live the Zoltan court, the most humane court in the Galaxy!”"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:176
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"Judging by the border guards who met you at the entrance to the sector, the "
"Zoltans do not intend to give up just like that, even if there are too few "
"of them to at least shorten the rebels for a short while."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:177
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""
"The Sectors of the Zoltans are always distinguished by exemplary order and "
"strict execution of laws.But with the arrival of the rebels, much will "
"change here ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:178
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[10]"
msgstr ""
"Remember, the main thing for the Claintans is the law and how it is "
"observed.You will follow their rules and maybe fly this sector without "
"additional \"adventures\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:179
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[11]"
msgstr ""
"Whether you will be met by the Zoltans peacefully or will you shoot you - it"
" only depends on you.But know that in connection with the war, the border of"
" their sector is vigilantly guarded ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:180
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[12]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan are the oldest race in the galaxy. Billions of years ago, they "
"transcended their physical bodies and took the form of pure energy. Though "
"they pride themselves on being a 'perfectly just' society, they can seem "
"amoral and condescending to other races."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:188
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"One Zoltan, who was seriously carried away by other people's races, "
"installed something like an alien shop of trinkets here.Why not look?"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:189
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The ship welcomes the ship: “My friends!I ask you, there is nothing that I "
"would have had nothing, that I wanted, but I could not get it.Please feel at"
" home, take a look at the goods. ”"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:190
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The mantis detachment took refuge in the belly of a long-dead space whale-"
"apparently, for them this is the only way to control the black market "
"without detection.Is it worth a look?"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:202
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Several asteroids rich in minerals were left \"for later\" by the local "
"Zoltans.It is a pity, but you do not have the necessary equipment to develop"
" them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:203
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You must admit - the territory of the Zoltans are actually a beautiful and "
"peaceful place.However, your main priority is the reload of FTL and the "
"completion of the mission, and not the inspection of the sights."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:204
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A small stream of asteroids is included in the atmosphere of the planet - "
"fireworks on a galactic scale.For him, this is a little, but you can admire "
"while you calculate the next jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:206
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You stumbled upon several Military ships of the Zoltans participating in "
"combat training.Their energy region is impressive, but notice how quickly "
"radiation and ion weapons are demolished."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:207
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You did not even have enough time to greet the Soltan ship, who was waiting "
"for something on this lighthouse before he left here.This is a very cautious"
" race."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:208
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"The shipyards of the Zoltans are located on this lighthouse.You admire, "
"observing hundreds of sparkling Zoltans, which perform thin work outside the"
" enormous transport ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:209
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"A broadcasting message from the nearest planet announces the presence of the"
" ancient monastery of the Zoltans, accessible to visit.Most likely this is "
"only a trick for tourists, however, you still do not have time for a visit."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:222
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your appearance almost prevented the Zoltansky Safety Savor, following the "
"mantis pirate in the asteroid field.They warn you: \"Your presence here is "
"still permissible, but please do not intervene.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:227
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Intervene and save the mantis ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:229
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes you must put on an outsider, even in those rare cases when it is a"
" mantis warship.You go to the center of the asteroid field and meet the "
"Zoltans with a battle."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:235
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Interchant and help the Cosltansa ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:237
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You catch up with the Claintans ship and intercept with it the mantis ship "
"in an asteroid field.Time to make new friends."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:243
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Do not interfere."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:245
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans know their affairs better than anyone - the best option would be"
" to leave them.You are preparing to jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:252
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_SHELL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrived at a huge, clumsy, no controlled ship of the Zoltans.It remains "
"a mystery what happened to the crew, but it would be a shame not to take "
"this opportunity."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:268
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrived at the Zoltansky shopping center - all that is needed for tired "
"travelers if they have the right documents."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:270
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Try to convince them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:274
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"teleporter\"]/text"
msgstr "(Teleporter) Transfer directly to the civilian platform."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:276
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"teleporter\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You materialized in the dark section of the main hall and are able to "
"conduct your research in peace."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:284
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ENERGY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Member of the crew of Zoltan) provide his official documents and pay an "
"entrance fee."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:286
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ENERGY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They scan the identifier of your Zoltan, in which he is designated as an "
"official citizen.Then they charge a fee and finally let you go on."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:297
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:299
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You do not have papers (or rather leather neuro-identification bracelets) "
"for entering inside, so it’s better not to try."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:307
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_TALK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"They rarely see the representatives of your species in these parts, and you "
"look like a Kasvagar sea glory in Pluto stroke from shrimp.You return to the"
" ship with a gang of the Zoltans on the tail!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:312
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_TALK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You introduced yourself as merchants and successfully went through the "
"gateway protection, however, this is only a matter of time, until someone "
"realizes that your identification cards are a fake!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:321
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You went to the supply store.This is a well -equipped self -service "
"store.The order is introduced into the terminal, a fee is charged from you, "
"and the purchase is dumped from the nearest gutter."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:328
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You went to the bar to find out the last rumors.The topics of conversations "
"here begin from the spread of microbes in the crop and end with joys from "
"the cruise of the pleasures of the collapse."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:332
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[2]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You overheard the conversation of one company that discovered the planet "
"before the first contact, and recorded its whereabouts."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:341
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrived on the primitive planet that you heard about in the bar, "
"completely not expecting to find the Claintans ship, who finds out relations"
" with the assault ship of the rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:345
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You tune in to their frequency and hear how the captain of the rebels "
"shouts: “We freed this planet in the name of the new Galactic "
"Government!These aliens will not remain in ignorance, no matter how they use"
" them. ”"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:347
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Intervene - make the first contact with primitive aliens."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:349
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The local population (fluffy, one -eyed tree creatures) began to sing "
"enthusiastically only seeing you.Suddenly, the sky was lit by a flash of a "
"laser - the Contributors opened fire on your ship!You rush back into the "
"ship and enter the battle."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:354
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"To protect aliens at the cost of life is to attack the ship of the rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:356
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"These creatures should be left to develop their own pace.You direct all the "
"tools to the rebels and get ready to open fire!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:361
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:363
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You do not want to warn about your presence of rebels, and even more so you "
"do not want to anger the Zoltans on their territory.The best solution is to "
"leave."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:380
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_AUGMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Academy of the Zoltans is attached right behind the perimeter of the "
"lighthouse.They are happy to show you the fruits of their work and offer you"
" to take something with them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:385
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_MAP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans, who are near this lighthouse, are happy to accept you and call "
"to visit on board.For formal reasons, they provided you with a tour of the "
"ship.In the process, some star maps caught your eye, the details of which "
"you, without hesitation, remembered visually."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:391
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/text"
msgstr "Something seems very strange to you in this moon in the distance."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:393
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "See what is there."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:397
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do not pay attention."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:399
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try not to focus on the moon visible in the scanner on the aft, and "
"continue to enter the coordinates of the next jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:403
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/text"
msgstr "(Boarding drone) Send a drone to sound the surface."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:405
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The trial scan immediately showed a network of caves shallow underground.You"
" launch an boarding drone, and it breaks through the surface into the cave "
"below."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:412
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your drone discovered a huge network of caves and evidence of past "
"excavations.Going down a little below, you found a gold scientist, still at "
"work.He tells you that all his colleagues have long been dead.You decide to "
"ask him a few questions and offer to join the crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:422
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"A more detailed study showed traces of life on the surface, nothing more "
"especially interesting."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:425
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"By sending a shuttle to study the mysterious system of caves, you discovered"
" traces of battle and still working weapons!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:429
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"A deep scanning of the surface showed a system of caves, extending to many "
"kilometers, and something similar to a mountain of scrap metal, remaining "
"from some very powerful mechanism."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:433
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the team can break through the thin layer of the lunar surface"
" into a hidden cave."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:435
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Try to blow up the explosives to break through the surface."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:437
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You lay explosives and go to a safe distance."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:448
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Explosives are too valuable to use it in archaeological work.Let's get out "
"of here."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:456
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Part of the surface layer is destroyed, and the impressive appearance opens "
"up as entire kilometers of the caves under you.You do not have time to "
"explore them all, but the remnants of the old underground base are still "
"worth visiting.Suddenly there is something useful ..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:460
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The explosives were undermined remotely, but the explosion did not lead to "
"anything.What a senseless waste of supplies."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:463
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your explosives opened the “cave”, which was actually a secret base located "
"in the hopper network right underground.All inside are dead;Apparently, not "
"so long ago, mantles visited here.It seems that the Zoltans were developing "
"an improved type of ship weapons.You take one of the best copies on your "
"ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:478
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The ship of the Zoltans is associated with you: “The nature of the day is "
"cyclical.The fever exhausts.The reason is ... ”They fell into some dangerous"
