"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the eye and peering into it.Suddenly you notice a stasis"
" capsule flying in your direction.You give the order to catch her and "
"deliver to the ship.In the capsule was Kristalin, who, after awakening, is "
"ready to serve you."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:803
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[7]/text"
msgstr ""
"Approaching the eye, you peer into it.A bright beam for a moment connects "
"your ship with an eye, and a young Zoltan appears behind the captain."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:807
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[8]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great eye, and he suddenly began to glow with a "
"green aura.The radiance begins to switch to your ship and forms a barrier "
"around it.With surprise, you understand that this is a Zoltan shield!You "
"thank fate and prepare for the departure."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:811
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[9]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great eye, and it begins to glow with bright red "
"light.Along with this, the temperature begins to rise rapidly, and now your "
"ship is embraced by a flame!You need to urgently get out of here!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:820
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[10]/text"
msgstr ""
"You turn the ship towards the eye and give the command to get closer.As soon"
" as it remains a few meters, it suddenly breaks into thousands of "
"fragments!A significant part of them stuck into the sheathing of your ship, "
"turning it into a sieve."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:853
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[11]/text"
msgstr ""
"The whole team begins to stare at the monolith.Strange, but no one can take "
"his eyes off.The effect of hypnosis lasts quite a long time.Having come to "
"your senses, you understand that the rebels during this time decently caught"
" up with you."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:857
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[12]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you are approaching the eye, a powerful flash cuts out space in "
"the direction of the rebel fleet.Telepatically, the eye made it clear to you"
" that your pursuers are now completely disorganized and will not catch up "
"with you soon."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:861
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[13]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great eye, but suddenly the sounds of a teleporting "
