"such gullible travelers like you.You are getting ready to fight back."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:865
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[14]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great eye and bring all the sensors on it.Suddenly, "
"the eye begins to vibrate, a small fragment breaks off and flies in your "
"direction.You give the order to charge the guns, but the fragment changes "
"the shape and turns into a weapon!You pick it up and prepare for departure."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:869
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[15]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great eye, and it begins to glow with black "
"light.Something strange begins to happen in your motor compartment-the fuel "
"tanks vibrate and heat up strongly.Fearing the explosion, you give the order"
" to drain part of the fuel.It seems to have worked, and the monolith "
"returned to the usual state again."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:875
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[16]/text"
msgstr ""
"You fly closer, and the Great Eye begins to shine with pure white light.This"
" light covers your ship, and you are surprised to observe how all the damage"
" to the body disappear.You thank fate and go to the next lighthouse."

