#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6510
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the eye and peering into it.Suddenly you notice a stasis"
" capsule flying in your direction.You give the order to catch her and "
"deliver to the ship.In the capsule was Kristalin, who, after awakening, is "
"ready to serve you."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6514
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[7]/text"
msgstr ""
"Approaching the eye, you peer into it.A bright beam for an instant connects "
"your ship with an eye, and a new crew member appears on the board of your "
"ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6518
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[8]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great Zolton eye, and he suddenly begins to glow "
"with a green aura.The radiance passes to your ship and forms a barrier "
"around it.With surprise, you understand that this is a Zoltan shield!You "
"thank fate and prepare for the departure."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6522
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[9]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great Zolton eye, and it begins to glow with a "
"bright red light.Along with this, the temperature begins to rise rapidly, "
"and now your ship is embraced by a flame!You need to urgently get out of "
"here!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6531
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[10]/text"
msgstr ""
"You turn the ship towards the eye and give the command to get closer.As soon"
" as it remains a few meters, it suddenly breaks into thousands of "
"fragments!A significant part of them stuck into the sheathing of your ship, "
"turning it into a sieve."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6564
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[11]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you are approaching the eye, a powerful flash cuts out space in "
"the direction of the rebel fleet.Telepatically, the eye made it clear to you"
" that your pursuers are now completely disorganized and will not catch up "
"with you soon."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6568
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[12]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are approaching the great Zolton eye, but suddenly the sounds of a "
"teleporting team and several explosions are heard!It seems that he turned "
"out to be a bait for such gullible travelers like you.You are getting ready "
"to fight back."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:6574
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTON_EYE_LIST\"]/event[13]/text"
msgstr ""
